                <xsd:annotation>
                        <xsd:documentation source="http://www.openapplications.org/oagis/10">The purpose of the GetItemMaster is to enable a business application module to request information concerning a specific ITEM from another business application.  The reply to this BOD is the ShowItemMaster.

